      "raw_text": "From the number of applications\nreceived from men employed by the\nWashington Water Power company\nthere will be large influx of new\nmembers, into tie Garments union\nat the next meeting of that or\nsanization. The men are still in\nhopes that the company will rein\nstate those discharged at the time\nthe union was organized 1t is\nclaimed that charges have been\nmade against the men by the Off\nGERS of the company which have\nnot been sustained as yet. In case\nTire charges are unfounded It is be-\nlieved the company will reinstate\nthe men to their old positions and\nranking."
